<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <div style="width: 100%; height: 100% background-color: white; color: #0F172A; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
    <div style="margin: 8rem auto; width: 80%; max-width: 400px">
      <h1>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">
        Welcome to <strong>Powerbase</strong>!
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">
        Powerbase provides a unified way to browse, manage, and interact with data stored across multiple systems - systems like your core user database, your customer CRM, and your no-code tools.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">To get started, please confirm your email address:</p>

      <table class="body-action" align="center" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 2rem 0;">
        <tr>
          <td align="center">
            <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
              <tr>
                <td align="center">
                  <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">
                        <a href="<%= @action_url %>" target="_blank" style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background-color: #4338CA; color: #fff; border-radius: 0.25rem; text-decoration: none;">
                          Confirm Email Address
                        </a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">
         If you didn&apos;t request this, please ignore this email. For questions you may have, feel free to <a href="mailto:<%= @support_email %>" style="color: #4338CA">email us</a>.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">
        Thank you,
        <br />
        Powerbase Team
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">
        If you&apos;re having trouble with the button above, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;">
        <%= @action_url %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
